posting_body: ['QUIET/PRIVATE/SAFE:', '3-room, garden-level space.', 'AVAILABLE: FRIDAY 8/12/22.', '5-minute walk to Mitchell-Hamline; or a 10-minute commute to United Hospital.', '$1200/mo; $600 (refundable) deposit.', 'Finished, semi-furnished, fully carpeted, 650 square foot,  garden-level space.', 'NON-SMOKERS ONLY & NO PETS.', 'INCLUDES:', 'WIFI, but tenant will need to arrange their  own cable hookup.', 'SEMI-FURNISHED BED/LIVING-ROOM: with large closet (built-in wardrobe & dresser); accessible egress window; bookshelves; dimmable-lighting.', 'Tenant encouraged to bring own bed*.', '*(There’s a futon couch/bed in the room at the present, but I highly recommend bringing own bed.', 'Futon will be removed.)', 'SECOND BEDROOM/NOW OFFICE:  with desk & chair; bookshelves; small file cabinet; accessible egress window; task- & dimmable lighting; leather chair & ottoman; large walk-in closet w/shelving & racks; new mini-refrigerator/freezer, microwave & toaster oven—never used;', '& a seldom used electric teakettle.', 'LARGE, PRIVATE, RECENTLY UPDATED BATHROOM WITH:         new toilet & shower/tub fixtures; washer/drying space; recently painted; new ceiling; ample storage.', 'ADDITIONAL PROVISIONS:', 'Separate garage stall with remote', 'Utilities: heat/electricity/water/snow/trash', 'TENANT REQUIREMENTS:', 'Background check—I will do; 3 solid references; renter’s insurance; current on COVID vaccinations; again, non-smoker.', 'NOTE: IF YOU HAVE ALLERGIES…there is a cat in the house who has access to this space; but the litter box is located on the main level, not in the rental space.', 'FOR APPOINTMENTS:', 'Text:', 'show contact info', '; NO VOICEMAILS.', 'SUBJECT LINE: #GreatForMitchellHamlineStudents—or—', '#GreatForUnitedHospitalInterns/Residents', 'PLEASE INCLUDE:', 'Phone # & background (CV)  information.', 'The address & exterior/interior photos will be made available after initial text communication/ interview.']
